Iss Pyaar Ko Kya Naam Doon? 3 (transl.What Shall We Name This Love? 3) is an Indian drama television series that aired on StarPlus from 3 July 2017 to 6 October 2017.[3] Produced by Gul Khan under 4 Lions Films, it starred Barun Sobti and Shivani Tomar.[4][5] The story is set in Allahabad and Mumbai. It is the third installment of the Iss Pyaar Ko Kya Naam Doon? series.
